    "description": "Stick Tournament is a Online Multiplayer 2D-Platformer, where you can compete against your friends in different levels.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 to 8 Players in Online Multiplayer</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 45 different levels</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The levels can be selected individually and you can choose a combination of your preferred levels yourself..</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can choose the number of total rounds and also adjust the overall speed for most of the levels.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You have the option to activate the voting menu and can vote on various effects (different running speed, change in gravity, ..) in the next level.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The Twitch integration allows your Twitch viewers to participate in this voting.</li></ul>",
